title: Steelers promote dual threat Tyler Murphy to active roster (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,510 Steelers promote dual threat Tyler Murphy to active roster (Yahoo Sports) PITTSBURGH (AP) -- The Pittsburgh Steelers promoted wide receiver/quarterback Tyler Murphy to the active roster Saturday, meaning it's likely Ben Roethlisberger won't play Sunday in Kansas City.
